<div class="w3-content" style="max-width:1100px;">
  <div class="w3-container w3-margin-top">
  </div>

    <div class="w3-row-padding">
      <div class="w3-twothird">
        <%= image_tag(@adventure.picture_url, width: '100%') if @adventure.picture.present? %>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-third">
        <h2><%= @adventure.name %></h2>
        <p><%= @adventure.location %></p>
        <p><%= @adventure.description %></p>
        <p>
          <%= link_to 'Update', edit_adventure_path(@adventure), :class => 'w3-btn w3-red w3-margin-top'  %>
          <%= link_to 'Delete', @adventure, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }, method: :delete, :class => 'w3-btn w3-red w3-margin-top'  %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="w3-container w3-margin-top">
    <h2>Be brave. Choose courage.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-row-padding">
    <div class="w3-third">
      <p>Finding your way around a new city (or country!) can be challenging but so rewarding when you finally find that cat cafe you've been searching for. Try not to get discouraged if you make a wrong turn or miss your exit. Everyone likes to be a hero, even Siri, so just ask for help and keep on exploring!<p>
        <hr>
        <h3>Tips for Using GPS</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Set your GPS before you leave.</li>
          <li>Make sure you also set your return destination (home, maybe?).</li>
          <li>If you're using your smartphone, mount it at eye-level so you aren't looking away from the road.</li>
          <li>Expect hiccups. Siri gets confused sometimes, just like us.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="w3-twothird">
      <%= image_tag "http://maps.google.com/maps/api/staticmap?size=450x300&sensor=false&zoom=16&markers=#{@adventure.latitude}%2C#{@adventure.longitude}" %>
      <div class="w3-container w3-white">
        <h3>Finding Your Way Here</h3>
        <p><b>Address:</b><br />
        <%= @adventure.address %></p>
        <p><b>Latitude and Longitude:</b><br />
        <%= @adventure.latitude %>, <%= @adventure.longitude %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w3-container w3-margin-top">
  </div>

  <div class="w3-row-padding">
    <div class="w3-third">
      <div class="w3-container w3-white">
        <h3>Have You Been Here?</h3>
        <p>What did you think? Was it kid- or pet-friendly? Care to share any tips?</p>
        <%= render 'comments/form' %>
        <br />
      </div>
    </div>


    <% @comments.in_groups_of(2) do |group| %>

    <div class="w3-third">
      <div class="w3-container w3-white">
        <% group.compact.each do |comment| %>
          <div>
           <p><%= comment.body %></p>
           <p><em>&mdash;<%= comment.user_name %></em></p>
           <p><%= link_to 'Delete', comment_path(comment), method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

      <% end %>

  </div>






  </div>



